description.content:
I will Build Video Sharing Websites Like YouTube, Dailymotion, Vimeo Clone.

 

This website is based on ads. Users can monetize their videos and Earn from their channel. You can put your ads inside the video also every type of add is supported here. their are lots of other features are available. Some Are Them are Listed Below

 

Main Features:

 

  • Upload Videos Easily
  • Channels: Users can create their channel and customize that according to his needs.
  • Points System (Where users can earn point by watching, commenting, uploading Videos)
  • Like, Comments, Subscriptions, Advertisement System, History, Watch Later, Pages.
  • Auto Import: Choose keywords, and thousands of videos will be imported from Dailymotion and also YouTube.
  • Monetization System: Users can monetize their contents.
  • Powerful Admin panel: You can manage all the settings and all the users from the administrators panel.
  • Private Messages System 
  • High Performance and Capability 
  • Videos Selling/Renting Feature 
  • Subscriptions System Available

If You Have Any Other Doubts Then Please Contact Me Through Inbox.
